=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好記得考前按仔同我地仲睇緊英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要成個econ post都係波台巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw我考完果日已經知自己一定係拎4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11a8b09d710d859a692da63f3e0e24ee3b09554","tid":47474,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-04T10:05:15.000Z","msg":"想知巴打econ 拎4有咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n17dse 都差唔多level 但想up 多個grade"},{"pid":"09f06aae6c138be1bf9a1a292d42bb0ef089a8c1","tid":47474,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-04T10:05:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知巴打econ 拎4有<span style=\"color: red;\">係</span>原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n17dse 都差唔多level 但想up 多個grade</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d441a9efb71c6d43787d4b6a660cf37d90837db4","tid":47474,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-04T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知巴打econ 拎4有咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n17dse 都差唔多level 但想up 多個grade</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我本身都係aim 5or above <br />\n咁其實我操卷所有野都好正常既<br />\nD long q 都接近95/120咁上下<br />\nMc就直頭操到45條tim(因為做到合埋眼都記得邊年邊題答案係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我自己都知出到去一定冇咁勁 我預38～40咁上下）<br />\n但之後考完mc我都知做得唔多好 一定冇38條 最後好似得35定34 睇返有幾條係唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後考完long q 就更加知收皮 因為我畫左price ceiling 做subsidy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係因為呢兩樣我就知自己4硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a44de65cf7fcde403aaf301d8351b424dd06416","tid":47474,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-04T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想知巴打econ 拎4有咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n17dse 都差唔多level 但想up 多個grade</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我本身都係aim 5or above <br />\n咁其實我操卷所有野都好正常既<br />\nD long q 都接近95/120咁上下<br />\nMc就直頭操到45條tim(因為做到合埋眼都記得邊年邊題答案係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我自己都知出到去一定冇咁勁 我預38～40咁上下）<br />\n但之後考完mc我都知做得唔多好 一定冇38條 最後好似得35定34 睇返有幾條係唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後考完long q 就更加知收皮 因為我畫左price ceiling 做subsidy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係因為呢兩樣我就知自己4硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我最後MC係39（扣走cancel果兩題<br />\nLQ好大機會最終死因係PP唔夠熟寫得唔夠detail<br />\n<br />\nbtw我鎚輸俾4424<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e12809213cded497eef7e865da121ea2cf4a18","tid":47474,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-04T10:48:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想知巴打econ 拎4有咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n17dse 都差唔多level 但想up 多個grade</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我本身都係aim 5or above <br />\n咁其實我操卷所有野都好正常既<br />\nD long q 都接近95/120咁上下<br />\nMc就直頭操到45條tim(因為做到合埋眼都記得邊年邊題答案係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我自己都知出到去一定冇咁勁 我預38～40咁上下）<br />\n但之後考完mc我都知做得唔多好 一定冇38條 最後好似得35定34 睇返有幾條係唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後考完long q 就更加知收皮 因為我畫左price ceiling 做subsidy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係因為呢兩樣我就知自己4硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我最後MC係39（扣走cancel果兩題）<br />\nLQ好大機會最終死因係PP唔夠熟寫得唔夠detail<br />\n<br />\nbtw我鎚輸俾4424<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n估唔到巴打得4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果日考完上高登睇返你係話岩左40條左右<br />\n我諗你一定5硬 但頭先睇到你得4都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLong q 既concept其實唔難 不過唔熟就真 我係對自己太有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甸恩真係痴撚線 果球我第一下係心諗仆街 宗師要比人紅出場？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知紅左西咸條友"},{"pid":"d0f56e37c343d04753d4d08d4cecff54588ad1b5","tid":47474,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T07:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想知巴打econ 拎4有咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n17dse 都差唔多level 但想up 多個grade</blockquote><